o have the opportunity to experience our brand and begin a free trial</li>\r\n	<li>People outside of our permission marketing channels aren’t aware of what the app</li>\r\n	<li>Current organic site visits account for 5% of traffic</li>\r\n	<li>Request our current users to rate the app in the app store will improve the app ranking and increase organic site visits to 7.5% within 45 days.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWhile having a great product is the most important success factor, a methodical and persistent approach to optimizing the customer funnels will further accelerate sales.', 'Simple Framework to Accelerate Revenue', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '248-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-08-12 07:37:55', '2014-08-12 07:37:55', '', 248, 'http://localhost/248-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
